Information We Collect We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, submit inquiries, or contact us for support. This may include: • Name and contact information • Account credentials • Property preferences and search history • Communication records How We Use Your Information We use the information we collect to: • Provide and maintain our services • Process your requests and transactions • Send you important updates and notifications • Improve our platform and user experience • Comply with legal obligations Information Sharing We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as described in this policy or as required by law. Data Security We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Your Rights You have the right to: • Access your personal information • Correct inaccurate information • Request deletion of your data • Opt-out of certain communications Contact Us If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@valuez.com. Changes to This Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
